    "patch_code": "int nextIndexOf(CharSequence seq) {\n    \n    char startChar = seq.charAt(0);\n    \n    /* Check if the starting character matches before looping through every index */\n    \n    for (int offset = pos; offset <= length - seq.length(); offset++) {\n        \n        boolean checkStartChar = true;\n            \n        for(int j = 0; j < seq.length(); j++){\n            if(seq.charAt(j)!=input[j+offset] ){\n                \n                checkStartChar=false;\n                break;\n            }  \n       }\n\n       if(!checkStartChar)continue;\n         \n        int i = offset + 1;\n        int last = i + seq.length() - 1;\n        \n        /* Check only until reaching the end of input array */\n        \n        if (offset < length) {\n            for (int j = 1; i < last && seq.charAt(j) == input[i]; i++, j++);\n            if (i == last) \n                return offset - pos;\n        }\n    }\n    return -1;\n}",
